{{version023}}
{{flavour|Conjures up a large cloud of roaring flames.}}

'''Flaming Cloud''' is a monster-only spell which covers an area in [[Cloud#Flame|flame cloud]]s and deals some impact damage. Barring fire resistance, this can be a serious threat.

{{monsters with spell}}

